name: International Women's Day Posters
description:
Happy International Women's Day 2020! We at Figma celebrated by sharing stories of inspiring women in our Slack. This is a set of posters you too can modify and print for your own space. And don't forget to call your mom.

--

International Women's Day (March 8) is a global day celebrating the social, economic, cultural and political achievements of women. The day also marks a call to action for accelerating women's equality.
